        <abstract>
            <p>Discusses table of Atlantic dust samples. Thinks dust came from South America.</p>
            <p>Discusses Patagonian tuff samples.</p>
            <p>Answers CD’s query about material from Pampas. Believes deposit made in brackish water.</p> 
<p>Criticises account of Atlantic dust in F. J. F. Meyen [<hi rend="italic">Reise um die Erde</hi> (1834–5)].</p> 
        </abstract>
